com.parse4cn1

Class ParseFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.parse4cn1.ParseFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.codename1.io.Externalizable, Parse.IPersistable

    public class ParseFile
extends java.lang.Object
implements Parse.IPersistable, com.codename1.io.Externalizable
    ParseFile is a local representation of a file that is saved to the Parse cloud.
